# 🚀 AI Resume–Job Match Analyzer

An intelligent AI-powered web application that analyzes a user's resume against a job description and provides real-time insights, match scores, personalized suggestions, and voice-based guidance.

---

## 🧠 Problem

Many students and job seekers apply for jobs without understanding how well their resumes match job requirements. This results in:

* High rejection rates ❌
* Lack of clarity about required skills ❌
* Time-consuming manual screening ❌
* No personalized feedback ❌

---

## 💡 Solution

AI Resume–Job Match Analyzer provides a smart and automated way to evaluate resumes.

It:

* 📄 Extracts text from resumes (PDF)
* 🧠 Identifies key skills using AI & NLP
* 📊 Calculates match score (%)
* ❌ Detects missing skills (skill gap analysis)
* 💡 Generates AI-powered suggestions
* 🗺️ Creates personalized learning roadmap
* 🎤 Provides voice-based explanation

---

## ✨ Features

* 🔍 Resume & Job Description Analysis
* 📊 Match Score Calculation
* ✅ Skill Matching & Gap Detection
* 💡 AI-based Suggestions
* 🗺️ Career Roadmap Generation
* 🎤 Voice-Based Explanation (AI Assistant)
* 🎯 Clean & Interactive Dashboard UI

### 🎤 Voice Feature

* Converts AI insights into speech
* Explains match score in a human-like manner
* Guides users on missing skills and improvements
* Enhances accessibility and engagement

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

### 🖥️ Frontend

* Next.js (React)
* Tailwind CSS
* Component-based UI

### ⚙️ Backend

* Next.js API Routes (Serverless)
* Node.js runtime

### 🤖 AI Integration

* OpenAI (GPT) for analysis & suggestions

### 📄 Data Processing

* PDF Parsing (pdf-parse / PDF.js)
* Custom Skill Extraction & Matching Logic

### 🗄️ Database

* Supabase (optional for scalability)

### 🛠️ Tools & Environment

* Vercel / Replit (Deployment)
* Git & GitHub (Version Control)
* VS Code (Development)

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

Frontend (Next.js UI)
→ API Route (/api/analyze)
→ Resume Parsing
→ Skill Extraction
→ Match Calculation
→ OpenAI Analysis
→ Voice Generation
→ Results Dashboard

---

## 📊 How It Works

1. Upload your resume (PDF)
2. Paste job description
3. Click "Analyze"
4. Get:

   * Match Score
   * Matched Skills
   * Missing Skills
   * AI Suggestions
   * 🎤 Voice Explanation

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

### 1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/ai-resume-analyzer.git
cd ai-resume-analyzer
```

### 2. Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

### 3. Add environment variables

Create a `.env.local` file:

```env
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
```

### 4. Run the application

```bash
npm run dev
```

